didn't you?

219
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,910
I'd forget if you hadn't reminded me.

220
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,870
Alright, I'm off.

221
00:12:18,030 --> 00:12:19,360
Everyone about your business.

222
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,840
Don't delay Mr. Gu's

223
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,200
precious family reunion.

224
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:23,870
Sure, sure.

225
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,800
Okay, okay.

226
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,230
Well, Mrs. Gu,

227
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,600
I have a family matter.

228
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,750
I'm leaving.

229
00:12:32,660 --> 00:12:34,160
I'll pick up the things later.

230
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:46,420
(Buao Alley)

231
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:51,440
There's nothing more I can do.

232
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,480
Leave here with your kid.

233
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:55,000
Now the whole neighborhood knows
I'm your wife.

234
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,390
That has quite an impact.

235
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,200
If you kick me out now,

236
00:12:58,510 --> 00:12:59,790
Commander Xiao will surely find out

237
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:00,960
that we are deceiving him.

238
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,080
Come on,

239
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,960
you have a husband and a kid,

240
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,320
but you still want to stay here.

241
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:08,150
Don't you have any shame?

242
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:16,440
In this world,

243
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,200
I just want to live well with my child.

244
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,140
(Buao Alley)
Am I wrong?

